---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="relative overflow-hidden bg-secondary text-white">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-25">
        <div
            class="absolute inset-x-0 top-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-primary to-transparent"
        >
        </div>
        <div class="absolute -right-24 top-10 h-64 w-64 rounded-full bg-primary/10 blur-3xl"></div>
        <div class="absolute -left-24 bottom-0 h-64 w-64 rounded-full bg-primary/5 blur-3xl"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-[1.4fr_0.9fr_0.9fr]">
            <div class="space-y-6">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                    <img src="/logo.png" alt="Tovarlabs" class="h-12 w-auto" />
                    <div>
                        <p class="text-xl font-bold tracking-wide text-primary">Tovarlabs</p>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Soluciones digitales a medida</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <p class="max-w-xl text-base leading-7 text-gray-300">
                    Diseñamos sitios, sistemas y automatizaciones con enfoque en velocidad, claridad
                    y resultados medibles para negocios que quieren verse y operar mejor.
                </p>

                <div class="grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-3">
                    <div
                        class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-4 py-3 backdrop-blur-sm"
                    >
                        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-gray-400">Enfoque</p>
                        <p class="mt-1 text-sm font-semibold text-white">Frontend profesional</p>
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-4 py-3 backdrop-blur-sm"
                    >
                        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-gray-400">Entrega</p>
                        <p class="mt-1 text-sm font-semibold text-white">A medida</p>
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-4 py-3 backdrop-blur-sm"
                    >
                        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-gray-400">Soporte</p>
                        <p class="mt-1 text-sm font-semibold text-white">Continuo</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div>
                <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-primary">
                    Navegación
                </h4>
                <ul class="mt-5 space-y-3 text-gray-300">
                    <li>
                        <a href="#inicio" class="transition-colors hover:text-primary">Inicio</a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="#servicios" class="transition-colors hover:text-primary"
                            >Servicios</a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="#tecnologias" class="transition-colors hover:text-primary"
                            >Tecnologías</a
                        >
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="#como-trabajamos" class="transition-colors hover:text-primary"
                            >Proceso</a
                        >
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="#contacto" class="transition-colors hover:text-primary"
                            >Contacto</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>

                <h4 class="mt-10 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-primary">
                    Stack
                </h4>
                <ul class="mt-5 space-y-3 text-gray-300">
                    <li>Astro para sitios rápidos y estables</li>
                    <li>Tailwind para una interfaz consistente</li>
                    <li>JavaScript ligero para interacciones clave</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div>
                <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-primary">
                    Contacto
                </h4>
                <ul class="mt-5 space-y-4 text-gray-300">
                    <li>
                        <a
                            href="mailto:info@tovarlabs.com"
                            class="flex items-center gap-3 transition-colors hover:text-primary"
                        >
                            <span
                                class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5"
                            >
                                <svg
                                    class="h-5 w-5"
                                    fill="none"
                                    stroke="currentColor"
                                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                                >
                                    <path
                                        stroke-linecap="round"
                                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                                        stroke-width="2"
                                        d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"
                                    ></path>
                                </svg>
                            </span>
                            <span>
                                <span
                                    class="block text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-gray-500"
                                    >Correo</span
                                >
                                <span class="block text-sm font-medium text-white"
                                    >info@tovarlabs.com</span
                                >
                            </span>
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a
                            href="https://wa.me/528143264788"
                            target="_blank"
                            rel="noreferrer"
                            class="flex items-center gap-3 transition-colors hover:text-primary"
                        >
                            <span
                                class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5"
                            >
                                <svg
                                    class="h-5 w-5"
                                    fill="currentColor"
                                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                                >
                                    <path
                                        d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413Z"
                                    ></path>
                                </svg>
                            </span>
                            <span>
                                <span
                                    class="block text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-gray-500"
                                    >WhatsApp</span
                                >
                                <span class="block text-sm font-medium text-white"
                                    >+52 81 4326 4788</span
                                >
                            </span>
                        </a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-14 border-t border-white/10 pt-8">
            <div
                class="flex flex-col gap-4 text-sm text-gray-400 md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between"
            >
                <p>&copy; {currentYear} Tovarlabs. Todos los derechos reservados.</p>
                <p>Diseño y desarrollo con foco en rendimiento, claridad y conversión.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</footer>
